<scope ilk="blob" lang="PHP" name="TestCase.php" src="/private/var/www/paperless/wp-content/themes/paperless-agent/iSDK/src/xmlrpc-3.0/test/PHPUnit/TestCase.php"><import line="23" module="PHPUnit/Assert.php" /><import line="24" module="PHPUnit/TestResult.php" /><scope classrefs="PHPUnit_Assert" doc="A TestCase defines the fixture to run multiple tests.&#10;&#10;To define a TestCase&#10;&#10;  1) Implement a subclass of PHPUnit_TestCase.&#10;  2) Define instance variables that store the state of the fixture.&#10;  3) Initialize the fixture state by overriding setUp().&#10;  4) Clean-up after a test by overriding tearDown().&#10;&#10;Each test runs in its own fixture so there can be no side effects&#10;among test runs.&#10;&#10;Here is an example:&#10;&#10;&lt;code&gt;&#10;&lt;?php&#10;class MathTest extends PHPUnit_TestCase {&#10;    var $fValue1;&#10;    var $fValue2;&#10;&#10;    function MathTest($name) {&#10;        $this-&gt;PHPUnit_TestCase($name);&#10;    }&#10;&#10;    function setUp() {&#10;        $this-&gt;fValue1 = 2;&#10;        $this-&gt;fValue2 = 3;&#10;    }&#10;}&#10;?&gt;&#10;&lt;/code&gt;&#10;&#10;For each test implement a method which interacts with the fixture.&#10;Verify the expected results with assertions specified by calling&#10;assert with a boolean.&#10;&#10;&lt;code&gt;&#10;&lt;?php&#10;function testPass() {&#10;    $this-&gt;assertTrue($this-&gt;fValue1 + $this-&gt;fValue2 == 5);&#10;}&#10;?&gt;&#10;&lt;/code&gt;&#10;&#10;@category   Testing&#10;@package    PHPUnit&#10;@author     Sebastian Bergmann &lt;sb@sebastian-bergmann.de&gt;&#10;@copyright  2002-2005 Sebastian Bergmann &lt;sb@sebastian-bergmann.de&gt;&#10;@license    http://www.php.net/license/3_0.txt  PHP License 3.0&#10;@version    Release: @package_version@&#10;@link       http://pear.php.net/package/PHPUnit&#10;@since      Class available since Release 1.0.0" ilk="class" line="80" lineend="258" name="PHPUnit_TestCase"><variable citdl="boolean" doc="@var    boolean&#10;@access private" line="85" name="_failed" /><variable citdl="string" doc="The name of the test case.&#10;&#10;@var    string&#10;@access private" line="93" name="_name" /><variable citdl="result" doc="PHPUnit_TestResult object&#10;&#10;@var    object&#10;@access private" line="101" name="_result" /><scope attributes="__ctor__" doc="Constructs a test case with the given name.&#10;&#10;@param  string&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="109" lineend="113" name="PHPUnit_TestCase" signature="PHPUnit_TestCase($name = FALSE)"><variable default="FALSE" ilk="argument" line="109" name="name" /></scope><scope doc="Counts the number of test cases executed by run(TestResult result).&#10;&#10;@return integer&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="121" lineend="123" name="countTestCases" returns="integer" signature="integer countTestCases()" /><scope doc="Gets the name of a TestCase.&#10;&#10;@return string&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="131" lineend="133" name="getName" returns="string" signature="string getName()" /><scope doc="Runs the test case and collects the results in a given TestResult object.&#10;&#10;@param  object&#10;@return object&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="142" lineend="147" name="run" returns="object" signature="object run(&amp; $result)"><variable ilk="argument" line="142" name="result" /></scope><scope doc="Runs the bare test sequence.&#10;&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="154" lineend="159" name="runBare" signature="runBare()" /><scope doc="Override to run the test and assert its state.&#10;&#10;@access protected" ilk="function" line="166" lineend="173" name="runTest" signature="runTest()" /><scope doc="Sets the name of a TestCase.&#10;&#10;@param  string&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="181" lineend="183" name="setName" signature="setName($name)"><variable ilk="argument" line="181" name="name" /></scope><scope doc="Returns a string representation of the test case.&#10;&#10;@return string&#10;@access public" ilk="function" line="191" lineend="193" name="toString" returns="string" signature="string toString()" /><scope doc="Creates a default TestResult object.&#10;&#10;@return object&#10;@access protected" ilk="function" line="201" lineend="203" name="createResult" returns="object" signature="object &amp;createResult()" /><scope doc="Fails a test with the given message.&#10;&#10;@param  string&#10;@access protected" ilk="function" line="211" lineend="228" name="fail" signature="fail($message = '')"><variable default="''" ilk="argument" line="211" name="message" /><variable citdl="debug_backtrace()" line="213" name="trace" /></scope><scope doc="Passes a test.&#10;&#10;@access protected" ilk="function" line="235" lineend="239" name="pass" signature="pass()" /><scope doc="Sets up the fixture, for example, open a network connection.&#10;This method is called before a test is executed.&#10;&#10;@access protected&#10;@abstract" ilk="function" line="248" lineend="248" name="setUp" signature="setUp()" /><scope doc="Tears down the fixture, for example, close a network connection.&#10;This method is called after a test is executed.&#10;&#10;@access protected&#10;@abstract" ilk="function" line="257" lineend="257" name="tearDown" signature="tearDown()" /></scope></scope>